<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5828934>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Compsomyces spp. A–B. C. lestevae Thaxt. A. Mature thallus showing antheridium (an) and perithecial wall cells (arrows). B. Immature thallus showing antheridium (an). – C–E. C. verticillatus (Thaxt.) Thaxt. C–D. Mature thalli. E. Detail of perithecium labelling eight wall cells (arrows). Scale bars: A–D = 50 µm; E = 20 µm. Photographs from slides ZMUC C-F-122939 (A–B), and ZMUC C-F- 124184 (C–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5828934/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

